{"tid":2067520,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"從六四到六一二 平凡人作出不平凡的承諾 義務律師林洋鋐如何走過三十一年的道路","createTime":"2020-06-17T05:16:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-17T05:27:48.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6caa9fa93aa85f2f9ea8de9a43e9fc4f8e3fa176","tid":2067520,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T05:16:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.mpweekly.com/culture/%E7%BE%A9%E5%8B%99%E5%BE%8B%E5%B8%AB-%E6%9E%97%E6%B4%8B%E9%8B%90-%E5%85%AD%E5%9B%9B-151633\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpweekly.com%2Fculture%2F%25E7%25BE%25A9%25E5%258B%2599%25E5%25BE%258B%25E5%25B8%25AB-%25E6%259E%2597%25E6%25B4%258B%25E9%258B%2590-%25E5%2585%25AD%25E5%259B%259B-151633&d=3WJ6yD1ie6zkJWt%2B9GiXG6CH8iT5eEApQhURqQe1KTk%3D&h=f0b36fbc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.mpweekly.com/culture/%E7%BE%A9%E5%8B%99%E5%BE%8B%E5%B8%AB-%E6%9E%97%E6%B4%8B%E9%8B%90-%E5%85%AD%E5%9B%9B-151633</a><br />\n<br />\n醫院內，三個警員，正看守一個傷者。<br />\n<br />\n義務律師林洋鋐趕到，要求與傷者單獨見面。打開布簾，一片血淋淋：背脊瘀黑、前臂骨折，傷口纏上了繃帶，雪白之中滲出一片紅。病牀上的傷者是一個年輕人，從警署轉送醫院。<br />\n<br />\n「你還有其他傷勢嗎？」林洋鋐問。<br />\n<br />\n年輕人緩緩抬起手掌，伸出五指，「食指骨折。」林洋鋐細看，骨頭已經突出，手指變形。林洋鋐點頭，吸了一口氣，重整思緒，為這個才二十歲出頭的年輕人提供法律意見。離開之際，林洋鋐忍不住回頭問一句：「你頂唔頂得住？」他準備請醫生巡房，看看有沒有稍減痛楚的方法。<br />\n<br />\n「我頂得住，林律師，你們都要頂住。」年輕人答。"},{"pid":"d30417f60425b7e1b9fa671d47a0c00b4128be92","tid":2067520,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T05:18:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81bca4d50bc5d9c108cbe0a98cddef6b8783c1b4","tid":2067520,"uid":174120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T05:20:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"857125a3a02e0f53d158006a3834236e78782ff7","tid":2067520,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"81bca4d50bc5d9c108cbe0a98cddef6b8783c1b4","tid":2067520,"uid":174120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T05:20:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T05:21:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2aaf119bfbb08ccfcf1c87e1da45be485e5cdc9d","tid":2067520,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T05:21:33.000Z","msg":"每一個都要頂住"},{"pid":"dc4b0c7f415082bf0848622407e1df44a47e9a3c","tid":2067520,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2aaf119bfbb08ccfcf1c87e1da45be485e5cdc9d","tid":2067520,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T05:21:33.000Z","msg":"每一個都要頂住"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T05:27:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}